<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nạ bdy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ̉nạ bdy ḥbk yạrby wạ̉ḥfẓ kl wṣạyạk bqlby
 bdy ṭyʿk bkl qlby wʿqly ạ̉nạ gẖlk tqblny yạrb
 rḥ ḍl rtl ạ̹lk yạrby tqbl ṣwty mʿ ạ̹ny ṣgẖyr
 bdy ḥbk mn kl qlby (bdy ḥbk)2 mn kl qlby
 yạrb lạ tsmḥ lḥd gẖyrk ydkẖl qlby ạ̉w ḥty̱ yfkr
 bdy ạ̹nt kl mạlk ḥyạty ạ̉nạ ạ̹lk tqblny yạrb
 lmạ yrtlk qlby byfrḥ ṣwty byʿlạ lḥty̱ ysmʿ
 bạltsbyḥ wạltmjyd bdy yhll ạ̉nạ ạ̹lk tqblny yạrb</lyrics>
